name: Bolha Chair
description:
BOLHA CHAIR, designed in 2025

This chair is part of the Bolha series with elegant wood-turned detailing and an upholstered seat. Crafted by skilled artisans in Northern Portugal.

Please inquire to view other wood options.

Production lead time: 6-8 weeks
